#
# Author: meshx project (in-tree patch)
# Authored against: mob_dev 0.4.0
# Updated: 2026-05-16
# Tracked by: apps/meshx_mobile_app/lib/mix/tasks/meshx.patch_deps.ex
# Background: docs/BLE_BRIDGE.md § "Build system note", project memory
#             [[mob-dev-ios-build-vendored-patches]]
